<HL>
   Navy Ship Contract Awarded
</HL>
<DATE>
07/11/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A4
</SO>
<CO>
   TDY
</CO>
<IN>
AEROSPACE (ARO)
</IN>
<GV>
DEFENSE DEPARTMENT (DEF)
</GV>
<LP>
   WASHINGTON -- U.S. Marine Management received a $161.5
million Navy contract for operating 18 ocean surveillance
ships.
                                                                                                       

</LP>
<TEXT>
   Teledyne Systems Co., a unit of Teledyne Inc., won a $15
million Navy contract for helicopter navigation systems.
