</SO>
<CO>
   ESEX WNEWS
</CO>
<LP>
   ESSEX Corp. (Alexandria, Va.) -- Harold P. Hanson was
named a director of this systems manufacturing and design
company. Mr. Hanson, 68 years old, succeeds Charles S. Smith,
44, who retired from the board to pursue other business
interests. Mr. Hanson is a former executive director of the
Committee on Science, Space and Technology of the U.S. House
of Representatives.
</LP>
